        "lead_headline": "The gut-skin axis research your dermatologist hasn't read yet.",
        "closing_quote": "Your mother had clear skin without a 10-step routine. Your grandmother never owned a serum. The difference isn't genetics or products — it's the microbiome they carried from home that you lost when your world changed."
